<article>
        <header class="post-header">
          <h2>The Basic Language of the Web: HTML</h2>

<div><img src="0714ffee-59ad-4e6a-8de0-21457f85bd9d.jpg" alt="0714ffee-59ad-4e6a-8de0-21457f85bd9d.jpg"  height="50"
            width="50"></div>
<p id="author">
            Posted by <strong>Laura Jones</strong> on Monday, June 21st 2027
          </p>
          <div><img src="578dcc8a-aa47-4211-be12-2a6aa5967596.jpg" alt="578dcc8a-aa47-4211-be12-2a6aa5967596.jpg"  width="500"
            height="200"
